original_title: Lyndon Arthur vs Walter Gabriel Sequeira
overview: Lyndon Arthur (19-1, 13 KOs) is planning on an explosive return to the squared circle as he looks to tame the tough Argentine, Walter Gabriel Sequeira (25-9-1) at Light Heavyweight as Wasserman Boxing heads to the University of Bolton Stadium for a massive night of boxing.
title: Lyndon Arthur vs Walter Gabriel Sequeira
